name: CanvasPlot
tagline: A JavaScript plotting library based on D3.js for visualizing large data sets
body:
# CanvasPlot

CanvasPlot is a JavaScript plot library that is able to interactively visualize large data sets by using the <canvas> element.

## Usage

To create a new plot...

	var plot1 = new CanvasDataPlot(d3.select("#maincontainer"), [1000, 900], {
		xAxisLabel: "IQ",
		yAxisLabel: "Test Score",
		markerLineWidth: 3,
		markerRadius: 5
	});
